### Health check
GET http://localhost:8080/health

### Login
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "document": "12345672930",
  "password": "pass"
}

### Create Account
POST http://localhost:8080/accounts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "document": "12346672930",
  "password": "pass"
}

